description: The 200 is a state-of-the-art smartphone designed to cater to the needs of tech-savvy users. It features a large 6.7-inch AMOLED display with high-definition resolution and True 1.07 billion colors for a visually stunning experience. The advanced triple rear camera system allows users to capture every detail with clarity, whether shooting expansive landscapes or intricate macro shots. Under the hood, the 200 is powered by a robust 3rd generation Snapdragon 7 processor, offering lag-free performance even during intensive use. The device is equipped with a 5200mAh 2nd Gen Silicon Carbon battery supported 100W Super Fast Charge, providing long-lasting battery life and rapid charging. Additionally, the 200 runs on AI-Powered MagicOS 8.0, which introduces a host of smart features and enhancements, making everyday tasks smoother and more interactive. With its sleek design the 200 not only performs excellently but also looks stylish in any setting.

description: Capture the best moments of your life with the 13MP + 2MP ultra sharp dual-lens camera. Up your selfie game with the 8MP front shooter with adjustable selfie toning light. The 14.47cm Honor FullView display with 18:9 aspect ratio delivers a bezel-less viewing experience for gaming, watching movies and online shopping. description: The Honor 9 Lite boasts a double-sided 2.5D glass, adding to its beauty. Watch movies, play games or shop online - every visual will be displayed in high definition on the 14.35 cm (5.65'') FHD+ display. The phone packs a 13 MP + 2 MP dual-lens rear camera system and PDAF fast focus for picture-perfect photos. Featuring a Kirin 659 octa-core processor, this phone is great for daily use, and it performs well even when you're playing resource-heavy games. Its 3000 mAh battery allows you to go a whole day on a single charge.

description: The Honor 9 Lite boasts a double-sided 2.5D glass, adding to its beauty. Watch movies, play games or shop online - every visual will be displayed in high definition on the 14.35 cm (5.65'') FHD+ display. The phone packs a 13 MP + 2 MP dual-lens rear camera system and PDAF fast focus for picture-perfect photos. Featuring a Kirin 659 octa-core processor, this phone is great for daily use, and it performs well even when you're playing resource-heavy games. Its 3000 mAh battery allows you to go a whole day on a single charge.

description: Meet the Honor 9i - world's first smartphone with Four Cameras and a Full View FHD+ Display. It comes with a 13 MP Dual Front Camera System* that boasts a wide f2.0 Aperture. Its Selfie Toning Flash and pro-like lighting options give your selfies Bokeh effect and pro finishes. Capture even the minutest of details with the 16 MP Dual Rear Camera System*. Powered by 4 GB of RAM and a 2.36 GHz Kirin 659 Octa-core Processor, this smartphone delivers a performance, that's smooth and fast. Its 64 GB of ROM offers you ample space to store many photos, songs, ebooks and much more. It takes advantage of EMUI 8.0 to offer you the Android Oreo features and security. Measuring just 7.5 mm, the metal unibody of Honor 9i has the lenses and the fingerprint reader placed strategically in a non-intrusive axis, so you can use the phone conveniently when you�re on the move.

description: The Honor 9 Lite boasts a double-sided 2.5D glass, adding to its beauty. Watch movies, play games or shop online - every visual will be displayed in high definition on the 14.35 cm (5.65'') FHD+ display. The phone packs a 13 MP + 2 MP dual-lens rear camera system and PDAF fast focus for picture-perfect photos. Featuring a Kirin 659 octa-core processor, this phone is great for daily use, and it performs well even when you're playing resource-heavy games. Its 3000 mAh battery allows you to go a whole day on a single charge.

description:
200MP Ultra-Clear Rear Camera, Master of Photography: HONOR 90 features a 200MP Ultra-Clear Main Camera with the largest 1/1.4-inch sensor in the segment, a 12MP Ultra Wide and Macro 2-in-1 Camera, and a 2MP Depth Camera and a 50MP Selfie camera and 100° wide FOV hardware to capture exquisite photos and videos.
120Hz Quad-Curved Floating AMOLED Display: The leading technology can correct the deform of images on the display, ensuring visual comfort. Equipped with a 6.7-inch/17.02cm quad-curved bezel-less display, HONOR 90 supports a high resolution of 2664x1200, 100% DCI-P3 color gamut, up to 1.07 colors, and segment leading peak HDR brightness of 1600 nits.
Risk-free Industry's first 3840Hz PWM Dimming: To promote eye health the HONOR 90 is equipped with the industry-leading Pulse Width Modulation (PWM) Dimming of 3840Hz, the highest in the industry, which maintains a more comfortable and flicker-free viewing experience and minimizes eye strain especially in dimly lit environments.
Extraordinary Performance: HONOR 90 is equipped with Qualcomm Snapdragon 7 Gen 1 Accelerated Edition 5G 4nm processor, which can provide exceptional performance and handle even the most intensive and demanding tasks with ease. The phone adopts a super-large arterial biomimetic VC with the Gen 3 high thermal conductivity graphite sheet and a full-scene AI intelligent thermal management system. Control temperature accurately, dissipate heat stably.
Honor MagicOS 7.1: Powered by Android 13, Magic OS 7.1 is an all-scenario smart collaborative OS. With extensive Google services like Google Voice Assistant, Google Chrome, Google Maps, and more, Honor 90 blends the best of both worlds. supports the "Link to Windows" feature, which allows Honor 90 users to connect their phone to the PC.

description:
200MP Ultra-Clear Rear Camera, Master of Photography: HONOR 90 features a 200MP Ultra-Clear Main Camera with the largest 1/1.4-inch sensor in the segment, a 12MP Ultra Wide and Macro 2-in-1 Camera, and a 2MP Depth Camera and a 50MP Selfie camera and 100° wide FOV hardware to capture exquisite photos and videos.
120Hz Quad-Curved Floating AMOLED Display: The leading technology can correct the deform of images on the display, ensuring visual comfort. Equipped with a 6.7-inch/17.02cm quad-curved bezel-less display, HONOR 90 supports a high resolution of 2664x1200, 100% DCI-P3 color gamut, up to 1.07 colors, and segment leading peak HDR brightness of 1600 nits.
Risk-free Industry's first 3840Hz PWM Dimming: To promote eye health the HONOR 90 is equipped with the industry-leading Pulse Width Modulation (PWM) Dimming of 3840Hz, the highest in the industry, which maintains a more comfortable and flicker-free viewing experience and minimizes eye strain especially in dimly lit environments.
Extraordinary Performance: HONOR 90 is equipped with Qualcomm Snapdragon 7 Gen 1 Accelerated Edition 5G 4nm processor, which can provide exceptional performance and handle even the most intensive and demanding tasks with ease. The phone adopts a super-large arterial biomimetic VC with the Gen 3 high thermal conductivity graphite sheet and a full-scene AI intelligent thermal management system. Control temperature accurately, dissipate heat stably.
Honor MagicOS 7.1: Powered by Android 13, Magic OS 7.1 is an all-scenario smart collaborative OS. With extensive Google services like Google Voice Assistant, Google Chrome, Google Maps, and more, Honor 90 blends the best of both worlds. supports the "Link to Windows" feature, which allows Honor 90 users to connect their phone to the PC.

description: Meet the Honor 9i - world's first smartphone with Four Cameras and a Full View FHD+ Display. It comes with a 13 MP Dual Front Camera System* that boasts a wide f2.0 Aperture. Its Selfie Toning Flash and pro-like lighting options give your selfies Bokeh effect and pro finishes. Capture even the minutest of details with the 16 MP Dual Rear Camera System*. Powered by 4 GB of RAM and a 2.36 GHz Kirin 659 Octa-core Processor, this smartphone delivers a performance, that's smooth and fast. Its 64 GB of ROM offers you ample space to store many photos, songs, ebooks and much more. It takes advantage of EMUI 8.0 to offer you the Android Oreo features and security. Measuring just 7.5 mm, the metal unibody of Honor 9i has the lenses and the fingerprint reader placed strategically in a non-intrusive axis, so you can use the phone conveniently when you�re on the move.

description: Stay productive and improve your performance with the Super Retina XDR display that is comfortable for the eyes. Powered with a 12 MP main camera, enjoy taking pictures with friends and family. With a built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery and equipped with the MagSafe wireless charging, you can charge your phone quickly up to 50 % in just half an hour by using a 20 W adapter. This phone is loaded with a horde of exciting features such as Siri, face ID, barometer, ambient light sensors etc., and is also resistant to dust and water as it is IP68 rated.

Plus, it's USB-C compatible, simplifying your charging needs. Elevate your tech game with the iPhone 15 – innovation at your fingertips. Goodbye cable clutter, hello convenience.

description: Experience the iPhone 15 – your dynamic companion. Dynamic Island ensures you stay connected, bubbling up alerts seamlessly while you're busy. Its durable design features infused glass and aerospace-grade aluminum, making it dependable and resistant to water and dust. Capture life with precision using the 48 MP Main Camera, perfect for any shot. Powered by the A16 Bionic Processor, it excels in computational photography and more, all while conserving battery life. Plus, it's USB-C compatible, simplifying your charging needs. Elevate your tech game with the iPhone 15 – innovation at your fingertips. Goodbye cable clutter, hello convenience.

description: Stay productive and improve your performance with the Super Retina XDR display that is comfortable for the eyes. Powered with a 12 MP main camera, enjoy taking pictures with friends and family. With a built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery and equipped with the MagSafe wireless charging, you can charge your phone quickly up to 50 % in just half an hour by using a 20 W adapter. This phone is loaded with a horde of exciting features such as Siri, face ID, barometer, ambient light sensors etc., and is also resistant to dust and water as it is IP68 rated.

description: Experience the iPhone 15 – your dynamic companion. Dynamic Island ensures you stay connected, bubbling up alerts seamlessly while you're busy. Its durable design features infused glass and aerospace-grade aluminum, making it dependable and resistant to water and dust. Capture life with precision using the 48 MP Main Camera, perfect for any shot. Powered by the A16 Bionic Processor, it excels in computational photography and more, all while conserving battery life. Plus, it's USB-C compatible, simplifying your charging needs. Elevate your tech game with the iPhone 15 – innovation at your fingertips. Goodbye cable clutter, hello convenience.

description: Experience the iPhone 15 – your dynamic companion. Dynamic Island ensures you stay connected, bubbling up alerts seamlessly while you're busy. Its durable design features infused glass and aerospace-grade aluminum, making it dependable and resistant to water and dust. Capture life with precision using the 48 MP Main Camera, perfect for any shot. Powered by the A16 Bionic Processor, it excels in computational photography and more, all while conserving battery life. Plus, it's USB-C compatible, simplifying your charging needs. Elevate your tech game with the iPhone 15 – innovation at your fingertips. Goodbye cable clutter, hello convenience.

description: Stay productive and improve your performance with the Super Retina XDR display that is comfortable for the eyes. Powered with a 12 MP main camera, enjoy taking pictures with friends and family. With a built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery and equipped with the MagSafe wireless charging, you can charge your phone quickly up to 50 % in just half an hour by using a 20 W adapter. This phone is loaded with a horde of exciting features such as Siri, face ID, barometer, ambient light sensors etc., and is also resistant to dust and water as it is IP68 rated.

description: Stay productive and improve your performance with the Super Retina XDR display that is comfortable for the eyes. Powered with a 12 MP main camera, enjoy taking pictures with friends and family. With a built-in rechargeable lithium-ion battery and equipped with the MagSafe wireless charging, you can charge your phone quickly up to 50 % in just half an hour by using a 20 W adapter. This phone is loaded with a horde of exciting features such as Siri, face ID, barometer, ambient light sensors etc., and is also resistant to dust and water as it is IP68 rated.

description:
A fine blend of great design and functional software that is designed to make full use of the hardware that it is fitted with, the iPhone 4 from Apple is one smartphone that you will keep coming back to.
HD Camera with LED Flash
The iPhone 4 comes with a 5 megapixel primary camera that is capable of HD recording and is aided by an LED flash that allows you to take great pictures even in low-light conditions. It also sports a 0.3 megapixel front camera to provide for video calling and good quality selfies for your next profile picture.
Multi-touch Screen
The smartphone comes with a 3.5 inch screen that allows you to use more than one finger at a time – you can get more work done by using multiple fingers to navigate. The screen also comes with oleophobic coating to ensure that visuals are not smudged with fingerprints and is also scratch-resistant to allow for longevity of the screen's receptiveness.
Longer Talktime of 14hrs
Built around a 1420 mAh Li-Ion battery, the iPhone 4 can give you a talktime of up to 14 hours on a 2G network – you can play a game to kill time or just browse the internet for interesting stuff to read on a long commute without worrying about finding a socket and charger every so often.
Built-in 8 GB Memory
This iPhone comes with an internal memory of 8 GB, making for ample space for your apps and media without worrying about slowing the phone’s receptiveness down.

Plus, it's USB-C compatible, simplifying your charging needs. Elevate your tech game with the iPhone 15 Plus – innovation at your fingertips. Goodbye cable clutter, hello convenience.

description:
Samsung Guru music 2 proves otherwise. It comes with 16 GB of expandable memory which is large enough to store up to 3000 songs. This phone also features an advanced MP3 player and powerful loudspeakers so you feel your music.
Tough in build and smart-looking by design, the Samsung Guru Music 2 stands for everything you love about feature phones. Experience the magic for yourself.
This feature phone’s vibrant 5.08 cm (2) screen is designed to enhance your viewing experience. Its sleek body hits the right spot when it comes to aesthetics.

description: The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G is a sleek blend of style and performance. Its stunning design, featuring Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+, and linear camera layout, sets it apart. Capture life's moments with the 50 MP wide-angle camera, even in low light, thanks to enhanced sensors. Record steady videos with Super HDR, OIS, and VDIS. Protect your data with Samsung Knox Vault, while enjoying the vibrant 16.83 cm FHD+ Super AMOLED display. Experience seamless multitasking with the improved GPU and NPU, and store all your content with a large internal storage. Stay connected longer with the 5000mAh battery and IP67-rated protection against spills and dust. Enjoy up to 5 years of security updates and easy data transfer with Smart Switch and Quick Share. With One UI 6, personalise your experience effortlessly. The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G: where style meets substance in a compact package.

description: The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G is a sleek blend of style and performance. Its stunning design, featuring Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+, and linear camera layout, sets it apart. Capture life's moments with the 50 MP wide-angle camera, even in low light, thanks to enhanced sensors. Record steady videos with Super HDR, OIS, and VDIS. Protect your data with Samsung Knox Vault, while enjoying the vibrant 16.83 cm FHD+ Super AMOLED display. Experience seamless multitasking with the improved GPU and NPU, and store all your content with a large internal storage. Stay connected longer with the 5000mAh battery and IP67-rated protection against spills and dust. Enjoy up to 5 years of security updates and easy data transfer with Smart Switch and Quick Share. With One UI 6, personalise your experience effortlessly. The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G: where style meets substance in a compact package.

description: The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G is a sleek blend of style and performance. Its stunning design, featuring Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+, and linear camera layout, sets it apart. Capture life's moments with the 50 MP wide-angle camera, even in low light, thanks to enhanced sensors. Record steady videos with Super HDR, OIS, and VDIS. Protect your data with Samsung Knox Vault, while enjoying the vibrant 16.83 cm FHD+ Super AMOLED display. Experience seamless multitasking with the improved GPU and NPU, and store all your content with a large internal storage. Stay connected longer with the 5000mAh battery and IP67-rated protection against spills and dust. Enjoy up to 5 years of security updates and easy data transfer with Smart Switch and Quick Share. With One UI 6, personalise your experience effortlessly. The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G: where style meets substance in a compact package.

description: The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G is a sleek blend of style and performance. Its stunning design, featuring Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+, and linear camera layout, sets it apart. Capture life's moments with the 50 MP wide-angle camera, even in low light, thanks to enhanced sensors. Record steady videos with Super HDR, OIS, and VDIS. Protect your data with Samsung Knox Vault, while enjoying the vibrant 16.83 cm FHD+ Super AMOLED display. Experience seamless multitasking with the improved GPU and NPU, and store all your content with a large internal storage. Stay connected longer with the 5000mAh battery and IP67-rated protection against spills and dust. Enjoy up to 5 years of security updates and easy data transfer with Smart Switch and Quick Share. With One UI 6, personalise your experience effortlessly. The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G: where style meets substance in a compact package.

The Galaxy A55 5G is more than a smartphone—it's a lifestyle companion designed for the modern world.

description: Experience the future with the Samsung Galaxy M16 5G in sleek Thunder Black. Enjoy lightning-fast downloads and seamless streaming thanks to 5G connectivity, keeping you ahead of the curve. description: The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G is a sleek blend of style and performance. Its stunning design, featuring Corning Gorilla Glass Victus+, and linear camera layout, sets it apart. Capture life's moments with the 50 MP wide-angle camera, even in low light, thanks to enhanced sensors. Record steady videos with Super HDR, OIS, and VDIS. Stay connected longer with the 5000mAh battery and IP67-rated protection against spills and dust. Enjoy up to 5 years of security updates and easy data transfer with Smart Switch and Quick Share. With One UI 6, personalise your experience effortlessly. The Samsung Galaxy A35 5G: where style meets substance in a compact package.

description: Showcasing the Redmi A3X: a stylish and innovative device. It is a visual joy thanks to its innovative premium Halo design and thin 8.3mm flat frame. Experience a cinematic display on this huge 17.04 cm (6.71) screen with a smooth refresh rate of 90 Hz and Corning Gorilla Glass protection. Safe and rapid access is guaranteed by the Face Unlock feature and the side-mounted fingerprint scanner. Multitasking and storage are effortless with up to 128 GB of extendable storage and 4 GB of RAM (plus 4 GB of virtual RAM). With the 8 MP AI dual camera and vintage film filters, you may take beautiful pictures. Powered by a Type-C charger and a 5000 mAh battery, you can use it all day. Take pleasure in superiority with the Redmi A3X.

description: Showcasing the Redmi A3X: a stylish and innovative device. It is a visual joy thanks to its innovative premium Halo design and thin 8.3mm flat frame. Safe and rapid access is guaranteed by the Face Unlock feature and the side-mounted fingerprint scanner. Multitasking and storage are effortless with up to 128 GB of extendable storage and 4 GB of RAM (plus 4 GB of virtual RAM). With the 8 MP AI dual camera and vintage film filters, you may take beautiful pictures. Powered by a Type-C charger and a 5000 mAh battery, you can use it all day. Take pleasure in superiority with the Redmi A3X.

With the 8 MP AI dual camera and vintage film filters, you may take beautiful pictures. Powered by a Type-C charger and a 5000 mAh battery, you can use it all day. Take pleasure in superiority with the Redmi A3X.

Experience mobile at its finest with the Redmi Note 13 5G, where innovation and quality collide.

The MediaTek Dimensity 6080 CPU powers lightning-fast 5G performance. Stays charged all day with a 5000 mAh battery and 33 W quick charging. Experience mobile at its finest with the Redmi Note 13 5G, where innovation and quality collide.

description: The realme C61, which offers unparalleled performance and longevity, is a masterpiece of engineering and design. The Octa-core CPU provides top-notch performance, and the 5000 mAh Massive Battery allows for longer usage. Use the 32 MP Super Clear Camera to capture breathtaking details. The realme C61 is a streamlined package that blends innovation, durability, and great performance.

description: Discover the amazing ultra-narrow bezel 120 Hz AMOLED display, ideal for gaming and streaming. With features like dual video recording and super night mode, the 32 MP front camera and 108 MP triple back camera allow you to take sharp pictures. With a 33 W fast charger, 15 W wireless charging, and a 5000 mAh battery, you can stay fueled. Smooth performance is provided by the MediaTek Dimensity 7020 5G CPU. Take advantage of MemFusion Virtual RAM, 256 GB of storage, 8 GB of RAM that can be expanded, and an elegant design with Active Halo Lighting. This feature-rich phone is completed with two JBL stereo speakers, IP53 certification, IR remote, and AI assistant Floax.

description: The Infinix Note 40 Pro+ 5G smartphone is a sleek and powerful device redefining mobile technology. With a clean UI and Active Halo AI Lighting, it offers a clutter-free and engaging experience. The 3D curved 120 Hz AMOLED display provides immersive visuals, while the in-display fingerprint unlock ensures convenient security. Capture stunning moments with the 108 MP OIS triple camera setup and recharge other devices with wireless reverse charging. Powered by a MediaTek Dimensity 7020 5G processor and Infinix X1 Cheetah Chip, it delivers unparalleled performance and efficient charging management. Dual JBL speakers offer immersive sound, complementing the premium design. Enjoy ample storage with up to 24 GB of RAM and 256 GB of ROM, while 100 W multi-speed fast charging ensures all-day usage. The Note 40 Pro+ 5G combines innovation, style, and reliability for an exceptional mobile experience.

description: This Infinix HOT50 5G combines style, performance, and reliability in one sleek package. With 7.8 mm slim premium design, this phone is not only easy to handle but also built to last, with its A Level TUV SUD rating. Capture every moment with clarity using the IMX582 clear camera, while the 4 GB RAM and 128 GB UFS2.2 storage ensure smooth multitasking and ample space for all your needs. Powered by the Dimensity 6300 5G processor, you’ll experience lightning-fast connectivity and powerful performance . With smart features powered by Infinix AI, you’ll enjoy a more personalized experience, Plus, it’s splash-proof with wet touch support, making it reliable in any weather. All of this runs smoothly on XOS 14.5, powered by Android 14, offering the latest features and a seamless user experience.

description: Discover the amazing ultra-narrow bezel 120 Hz AMOLED display, ideal for gaming and streaming. With features like dual video recording and super night mode, the 32 MP front camera and 108 MP triple back camera allow you to take sharp pictures. With a 33 W fast charger, 15 W wireless charging, and a 5000 mAh battery, you can stay fueled. Smooth performance is provided by the MediaTek Dimensity 7020 5G CPU. Take advantage of MemFusion Virtual RAM, 256 GB of storage, 8 GB of RAM that can be expanded, and an elegant design with Active Halo Lighting. This feature-rich phone is completed with two JBL stereo speakers, IP53 certification, IR remote, and AI assistant Floax.

description: Explore a range of new features on this Oppo Reno 10 5G smartphone. Capture interesting snaps with the ultra clear Portrait camera. This phone has a 64 MP main camera, 32 MP Telephoto camera, 32 MP selfie camera and a 112 degree wide-angle camera. This sleek phone weighs only about 185 g and has a 3D curved screen with 120 Hz. Powered with a 5000 mAh battery and 67 W SUPERVOOC charger, this phone runs for an entire day. This Oppo smartphone is equipped with MediaTek Dimensity 7050 SoC Processor and comprises a powerful computing engine. You can explore other features on this phone such as dual stereo speakers, screencast feature, IR remote control, smart AOD functionality and Auto Pixelate for safe file transferring.

description: For the contemporary consumer, has created a robust and stylish smartphone with the A3 Pro 5G. It has a 5100 mAh Hyper-energy Battery that lasts more than four years, a 45 W SUPERVOOCTM Flash Charge for quick charging, and a 360° Damage-proof Armour Body. Even in direct sunlight, the 120 Hz Ultra Bright Display provides bright, crisp images. With AI LinkBoost for flawless connectivity, AI Eraser for flawless photographs, and Ultra Volume Mode for clear conversations in busy conditions, it guarantees optimal performance. Beautiful photographs are captured by the 50 MP AI Main Camera and AI Portrait Retouching, while seamless multitasking is ensured by the MediaTek Dimensity 6300 5G processor and RAM Expansion. Savour the exquisite style and robust Anti-drop Shield Case for all-around pleasure.

description: For the contemporary consumer, Oppo has created a robust and stylish smartphone with the A3 Pro 5G. It has a 5100 mAh Hyper-energy Battery that lasts more than four years, a 45 W SUPERVOOCTM Flash Charge for quick charging, and a 360° Damage-proof Armour Body. Even in direct sunlight, the 120 Hz Ultra Bright Display provides bright, crisp images. With AI LinkBoost for flawless connectivity, AI Eraser for flawless photographs, and Ultra Volume Mode for clear conversations in busy conditions, it guarantees optimal performance. Beautiful photographs are captured by the 50 MP AI Main Camera and AI Portrait Retouching, while seamless multitasking is ensured by the MediaTek Dimensity 6300 5G processor and RAM Expansion. Savour the exquisite style and robust Anti-drop Shield Case for all-around pleasure.

product_name: ASUS Zenfone Max Pro M1 (Grey, 32 GB)
description: With a massive 5000 mAh battery, a powerful Qualcomm Snapdragon 636 processor and an Adreno 509 GPU, the Zenfone Max Pro (M1) packs quite a punch. Its 15.21 cm (5.99) FHD + Full View Display, along with its 2nd generation NXP SMART Amplifier and 5-magnet Speaker, takes your audiovisual experience to the next level. Equipped with a stock version of Android and the Android Oreo 8.1 operating system, this phone offers you a seamless and a more secure mobile experience. In addition, its Dual-camera System helps you take beautiful photos in almost any lighting condition. All of these awe-worthy features are packed within a compact Metal Body, making this phone robust and easy to hold.

description: Don’t you hate it when you are having an urgent discussion with your boss and your phone goes dead? description: The Vivo T3 5G: the pinnacle of speed, innovation, and creativity. Powered by the MediaTek Dimensity 7200 chip, it's a fast smartphone, scoring 734+ on AnTuTu. With the segment's first Sony IMX882 OIS sensor, clear shots are guaranteed, even in low light. Immerse yourself in the 16.94 cm (6.67) 120 Hz Ultra Vision AMOLED display, unlocking a cinematic experience. Dual stereo speakers and a 5000 mAh battery with 44 W FlashCharge ensure an immersive audiovisual journey that lasts. Capture every moment with ultra-stable 4K video and super night portrait mode. Plus, enjoy seamless multitasking with 8 GB RAM and memory booster features. Elevate your mobile experience with the Vivo T3 5G, where speed meets innovation.

Immerse yourself in the 16.94 cm (6.67) 120 Hz Ultra Vision AMOLED display, unlocking a cinematic experience. Dual stereo speakers and a 5000 mAh battery with 44 W FlashCharge ensure an immersive audiovisual journey that lasts. Capture every moment with ultra-stable 4K video and super night portrait mode. Plus, enjoy seamless multitasking with 8 GB RAM and memory booster features. Elevate your mobile experience with the Vivo T3 5G, where speed meets innovation.

Features: Crisp & Clear Full AMOLED Display -M7 fitness band uses the latest AMOLED technology in display hardware which provides excellent contrast and a visually stunning screen viewing experience, with a screen of 0.96 inches so that you get all the details you want. Long Battery Life- use more charge less, our new M7 fitness band does not require any charging for 7 days and can standby for 10 days, it can be fully charged within 2 hrs so that you use it more and care less about charging. Real Time Activity Tracking- The band keeps tracking your data round the clock without you noticing it and can store the data for 7 days without needing to sync. Battery Battery Capacity: 90mAh Standby Time: 0.

description: Presenting the quickest smartphone in its class, the IQOO Z7 Pro 5G. With its 4nm process-powered Dimensity 7200 5G CPU, it guarantees optimal performance and efficiency. A 17.22 cm (6.78 inch) 120 Hz AMOLED FHD+ screen with 1.07 billion colours and 1300 nits of brightness is included on the 3D Curved Super-vision Display. It has a Premium AG Matte Glass finish and is only 7.36 mm thick. With its 4K video recording capability and Super Night Mode, the 64 MP AURA Light OIS Camera allows you to take breathtaking pictures. With a Liquid Cooling System and 66 W FlashCharge, it offers maximum gaming performance and sustained power. With the IQOO Z7 Pro 5G, you can experience speed, flair, and refinement.

description:
* Segment’s Fastest smartphone: Powered by the 4nm Snapdragon 8s Gen 4, Neo 10 hits an AnTuTu score of 2.42Mn+, delivering top-tier speed and performance
* Segment’s Slimmest 7000mAh battery*: Get powerhouse endurance with a 7000mAh Silicon BlueVolt Battery* and 120W FlashCharge*, all in an 8.09mm ultra-slim, lightweight design
* Segment’s highest 144 FPS gaming smartphone: Enjoy ultra-smooth, low-latency gaming with segment-leading 144 FPS performance, enhanced visuals, and better power efficiency

* 50MP OIS Portrait Camera: Shoot stunning portraits and videos with a 50MP sensor, 4K 60fps Rear and Front video recording, and built-in OIS for pro-level stability. Smarter AI Features such as AI Erase, Circle to Search, AI Image Expander, AI Photo Enhance, and more

product_name: Frontech - 55.88 cm (22 inch) HD LED Backlit VA Panel Monitor (MON_0060)
description: Upgrade your viewing experience with our LED Monitor. With a sleek 22" HD display and a resolution of 1920 X 1080, this monitor delivers crisp and clear visuals, making it ideal for both work and entertainment purposes. The VGA and HDMI interfaces allow for versatile connectivity, ensuring compatibility with various devices such as computers, laptops, gaming consoles, and media players. The wall-mountable design of this monitor offers flexibility in placement, helping you save valuable desk space and achieve the perfect viewing angle. Whether you're gaming, watching movies, or working on creative projects, the quick 2ms response time ensures smooth motion and reduces motion blur, providing an immersive and enjoyable experience. Our LED Monitor is not only visually impressive but also energy-efficient. The LED backlight technology provides excellent display performance while consuming only 21W of power, saving energy and reducing utility costs. The monitor also features a power indication LED, allowing you to easily check its status. With a 1-year warranty, you can have peace of mind knowing that your investment is protected. Our LED Monitor is designed with quality in mind, featuring two PCBs (Power & AD Board) and separate display panel power for reliable performance. The manual operation keys (Manu, Next, Previous, Power, Auto) offer convenient control over various settings. Experience the difference with our LED Monitor and enjoy an enhanced viewing experience with stunning visuals, versatile connectivity, and energy-efficient performance. Upgrade your workspace today!

description: Discover the Moto G85 5G, which has a revolutionary 3D Curved pOLED 120 Hz Display protected by Gorilla Glass 5 for remarkable longevity. With the 50 MP OIS Sony LYTIA 600 Camera system, you can take beautiful pictures in any kind of illumination. Utilise Smart Connect to share content with ease and make use of the built-in 12 GB RAM and 256 GB storage. Immersive sound is produced by its Dolby Atmos Dual Stereo Speakers, and its Snapdragon 6s Gen 3 engine guarantees lightning-fast 5G speeds over 13 bands. Android 14 delivers the newest advancements in mobile technology and security, with a 5000 mAh battery and 33 W TurboPower charging.

description: Discover the Moto G85 5G, which has a revolutionary 3D Curved pOLED 120 Hz Display protected by Gorilla Glass 5 for remarkable longevity. With the 50 MP OIS Sony LYTIA 600 Camera system, you can take beautiful pictures in any kind of illumination. Immersive sound is produced by its Dolby Atmos Dual Stereo Speakers, and its Snapdragon 6s Gen 3 engine guarantees lightning-fast 5G speeds over 13 bands. description: Discover the Moto G85 5G, which has a revolutionary 3D Curved pOLED 120 Hz Display protected by Gorilla Glass 5 for remarkable longevity. With the 50 MP OIS Sony LYTIA 600 Camera system, you can take beautiful pictures in any kind of illumination. Utilise Smart Connect to share content with ease and make use of the built-in 12 GB RAM and 256 GB storage. Immersive sound is produced by its Dolby Atmos Dual Stereo Speakers, and its Snapdragon 6s Gen 3 engine guarantees lightning-fast 5G speeds over 13 bands. Android 14 delivers the newest advancements in mobile technology and security, with a 5000 mAh battery and 33 W TurboPower charging.

description: Discover the Moto G85 5G, which has a revolutionary 3D Curved pOLED 120 Hz Display protected by Gorilla Glass 5 for remarkable longevity. With the 50 MP OIS Sony LYTIA 600 Camera system, you can take beautiful pictures in any kind of illumination. Immersive sound is produced by its Dolby Atmos Dual Stereo Speakers, and its Snapdragon 6s Gen 3 engine guarantees lightning-fast 5G speeds over 13 bands. Android 14 delivers the newest advancements in mobile technology and security, with a 5000 mAh battery and 33 W TurboPower charging.

product_name: TP-Link Archer C6 MU-MIMO Gigabit Wireless Router 2.4 GHz, 5 GHz 1200 Mbps Wifi Speed Dual Band Extern...
description: The MU-MIMO and Gigabit-capable AC1200 Wi-Fi router increases productivity by sending data at double the speed to numerous devices at once. With 867Mbps on the 5GHz band for gaming and streaming and 400Mbps on the 2.4GHz band for daily work, the Archer C6 Wi-Fi utilises 802.11ac technology. It has four external antennas for broad coverage and enhanced network protection with sophisticated WPA3 security. With beamforming technology, signal intensity towards identified devices is increased. It supports numerous devices without latency thanks to MU-MIMO, and gigabit ports provide rates that are up to 10 times faster than those of regular Ethernet. A complete home mesh network is made possible by EasyMesh compatibility, and adding more wireless devices to a wired network is made possible by Access Point Mode. With the Tether app for iOS and Android, setup and administration are simple.

description: GOPON-1000R-WONU GPON ONU is one of the XPON optical network unit design to meet the requirement of the broadband access network – works with both GPON as well as EPON. It is used in FTTH/FTTO to provide the data and video service This unit provides higher bandwidth and higher efficiency using larger, variable-length packets. It offers efficient packaging of user traffic, with frame segmentation allowing higher quality of service (QOS) for delay-sensitive voice and video communications traffic. It provides the reliability and performance expected for business services and provides an attractive way to deliver residential services. It enables Fiber To The Home (FTTH) deployments economically resulting to accelerated growth worldwide. Fully compatible with IEEE802.3ah Support port-based rate limitation and bandwidth control In compliant with IEEE802.3ah Standard Up to 20KM transmission Distance. Supports data encryption, group broadcasting, port Vlan separation, etc. Supports Dynamic Bandwidth Allocation (DBA) Supports ONU auto-discovery/Link detection/remote upgrade of software; Supports VLAN division and user separation to avoid broadcast storm; Supports power-off alarm function, easy for link problem detection. Supports broadcasting storm resistance function. Supports port isolation between different ports.  Supports ACL and SNMP to configure data packet filter flexibly. Specialized design for system breakdown prevention to maintain stable system. Supports software online upgrading EMS network management based on SNMP, convenient for maintenance.
